                        <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#sent?compose=new" class="ui button blue" type="submit"><i class="ui icon reply"></i> Répondre par email</a>
                        
                      
                        
                        
                        <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#sent" class="ui button orange" type="submit"><i class="ui icon close"></i> Annuler</a>
